author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 

Watch to see the full session of Astralblak (formerly ZULUZULUU), featuring previously unreleased footage, from when they visited the The Current studio back in 2016.

Songs Performed 
00:00:00 What’s The Price
00:04:10 Fades
00:08:30 Fall Behind
00:11:48 On Our Way

Musicians
MMYYKK – vocals, synths
Proper-T – vocals, keyboard
Greg Grease – vocals, beats, percussion
Trelly Mo – keyboard
DJ Just Nine – turntables

Credits
Engineer – Mike DeMark
Producer – Andrea Swensson
Visuals  – Nate Ryan
Digital Producer – Natalia Toledo
Graphics – Natalia Toledo

The Current’s Live Sessions Vault is supported by the Minnesota Orchestra, GS Motors, and Delta Dental of Minnesota Foundation.
